room_title: Escape room "1920’s Paris: A Moveable Mystery" by Riddle in Mashpee
review: I've been going to Escape the Mystery Room in Kingston, MA for a while and decided to try Riddle as there have been too many inconsistencies and missing pieces. Riddle is amazing! I did Paris with a friend and though we didn't escape it was really cool and fun! I will definitely be coming back! I love this place!

room_title: Escape room "1920’s Paris: A Moveable Mystery" by Riddle in Mashpee
review: We had an awesome time here! The Paris room was so fun. Our Game master Aaron was the best!
